---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Container from '../components/Container.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Use - QualifyMe">
  <main class="space-y-20 mb-20">
    {/* Header Section */}
    <section class="relative pt-36">
      <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 grid grid-cols-2 -space-x-52 opacity-40 dark:opacity-20">
        <div class="blur-[106px] h-56 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-purple-400 dark:from-blue-700"></div>
        <div class="blur-[106px] h-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-sky-300 dark:to-indigo-600"></div>
      </div>
      <Container>
        <div class="relative text-center mx-auto lg:w-2/3">
          <h1 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">Terms of Use</h1>
          <p class="mt-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg">
            Please read these terms carefully before using QualifyMe's AI-driven hiring platform.
          </p>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </section>

    {/* Terms Content */}
    <section class="py-20">
      <Container>
        <div class="mx-auto prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-4xl">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 p-8 md:p-12">
            
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
              <strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 2025
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-8">
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  By accessing and using QualifyMe ("the Service"), you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. If you do not agree to abide by the above, please do not use this service.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                  QualifyMe is an AI-driven hiring assistant platform that provides automated candidate screening, assessment, and evaluation services to help organizations streamline their recruitment process.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  QualifyMe provides AI-powered hiring solutions including but not limited to:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li>Automated candidate screening and assessment</li>
                  <li>AI-driven interview analysis and scoring</li>
                  <li>Skills evaluation and competency matching</li>
                  <li>Recruitment workflow automation</li>
                  <li>Candidate ranking and recommendation systems</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  As a user of QualifyMe, you agree to:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li>Provide accurate and complete information when creating your account</li>
                  <li>Maintain the confidentiality of your account credentials</li>
                  <li>Use the service in compliance with all applicable laws and regulations</li>
                  <li>Respect the privacy and rights of candidates being evaluated</li>
                  <li>Not attempt to reverse engineer or compromise the AI algorithms</li>
                  <li>Ensure fair and non-discriminatory hiring practices</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">4. Data Usage and Privacy</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  QualifyMe processes candidate data and organizational information to provide our AI-driven hiring services. By using our platform:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li>You consent to the processing of candidate data for hiring evaluation purposes</li>
                  <li>You ensure you have proper consent from candidates for data processing</li>
                  <li>You agree to our data retention and security practices</li>
                  <li>You acknowledge that AI analysis may involve automated decision-making</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-4">
                  For detailed information about how we handle data, please review our <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">5. AI and Algorithm Limitations</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  While QualifyMe's AI technology is designed to assist in hiring decisions, users acknowledge that:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li>AI recommendations are tools to assist human decision-making, not replace it</li>
                  <li>Final hiring decisions remain the responsibility of the hiring organization</li>
                  <li>AI systems may have limitations and potential biases that should be considered</li>
                  <li>Results should be validated against legal and ethical hiring standards</li>
                  <li>The service does not guarantee specific hiring outcomes</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">6. Payment and Subscription</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  QualifyMe operates on a subscription basis. Payment terms include:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li>Fees are charged according to your selected subscription plan</li>
                  <li>Payment is due in advance for each billing period</li>
                  <li>Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled</li>
                  <li>Refunds are subject to our refund policy</li>
                  <li>Late payments may result in service suspension</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  QualifyMe and its AI technology, algorithms, and platform are protected by intellectual property rights. You agree that:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li>QualifyMe retains all rights to its proprietary technology and algorithms</li>
                  <li>You may not copy, modify, or distribute our software or AI models</li>
                  <li>Your data remains your property, subject to our privacy policy</li>
                  <li>Any feedback or suggestions become property of QualifyMe</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  QualifyMe provides its services "as is" and disclaims warranties to the fullest extent permitted by law. We are not liable for:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li>Hiring decisions made based on AI recommendations</li>
                  <li>Indirect, consequential, or punitive damages</li>
                  <li>Loss of profits, data, or business opportunities</li>
                  <li>Technical issues or service interruptions</li>
                  <li>Third-party integrations or services</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">9. Termination</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  Either party may terminate this agreement:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                  <li>With 30 days written notice for convenience</li>
                  <li>Immediately for breach of terms</li>
                  <li>Upon non-payment of fees</li>
                  <li>For violation of acceptable use policies</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-4">
                  Upon termination, access to the service will cease and data may be deleted according to our retention policy.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">10. Governing Law</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                  These terms are governed by the laws of [Jurisdiction] without regard to conflict of law principles. Any disputes will be resolved through binding arbitration or in the courts of [Jurisdiction].
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">11. Changes to Terms</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                  QualifyMe reserves the right to modify these terms at any time. We will notify users of significant changes via email or platform notification. Continued use of the service after changes constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">12. Contact Information</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                  For questions about these terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@qualifyme.ai" class="text-primary hover:underline">legal@qualifyme.ai</a> or through our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact page</a>.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>